---
title: Double-Stacked French Dip Burgers with Aged Cheddar Cheese and Caramelized Onions
description: Hello French Dip! This classic all-American sammie is sandwiched between garlic buns with caramelized onions and melted aged cheddar cheese. Don't forget the bistro side salad to finish off this mouthwatering meal!
